  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When an enemy within 10 feet of you targets a creature other than you that you can see or hear with an attack or harmful spell, you may take a Reaction to make the enemy roll a Wisdom saving throw (DC = 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Charisma modifier). On a failed save, the enemy must choose you as the new target or lose the attack or spell. The effect does not protect from area effects, such as the explosion of a fireball.</p><p>Furthermore, you have Resistance to any damage received as a result of this attack or spell.</p>",
